{
  "3196520": {
    "name": "海岛机器人农场",
    "steam_appid": 3196520,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>海岛机器人农场</strong>是一款休闲<strong>放置挂机</strong>类农场模拟游戏。机器人可自动化种植、生产农产品、饲养动物、建造各种建筑来自由发展这座超大岛屿。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/e67bef6246c36c4fb45c40fb4689dffd.poster.avif?t=1765162952\" width=800 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/e67bef6246c36c4fb45c40fb4689dffd.webm?t=1765162952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/e67bef6246c36c4fb45c40fb4689dffd.mp4?t=1765162952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>你可以随时调整游戏窗口的大小，将它放置在屏幕的角落或底部，当你在处理其他事务时，机器人会默默建设你的海岛。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/dfbf4f19b625f0ea942f9f2b945d937a.poster.avif?t=1765162952\" width=668 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/dfbf4f19b625f0ea942f9f2b945d937a.webm?t=1765162952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/dfbf4f19b625f0ea942f9f2b945d937a.mp4?t=1765162952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自动化机器人：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个机器人都有不同的能力，合理分配任务能更高效地推动岛屿的发展。机器人可以自动化的工作，也可以选择让它们随机处理岛屿上的各种事务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/8fca29cd33712efcf641e5fd03c06a1e.poster.avif?t=1765162952\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/8fca29cd33712efcf641e5fd03c06a1e.webm?t=1765162952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/8fca29cd33712efcf641e5fd03c06a1e.mp4?t=1765162952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索外星植物：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了地球本土植物外，在游戏中还能够建造火箭，去往外星探索新植物，并带回来种在你的农场中。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/ce28fd96a58f09e9a3cd9515d17bfc18.poster.avif?t=1765162952\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/ce28fd96a58f09e9a3cd9515d17bfc18.webm?t=1765162952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/ce28fd96a58f09e9a3cd9515d17bfc18.mp4?t=1765162952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/3e60877e80c72aeaf2e7fbcce9c14480.poster.avif?t=1765162952\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/3e60877e80c72aeaf2e7fbcce9c14480.webm?t=1765162952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/3e60877e80c72aeaf2e7fbcce9c14480.mp4?t=1765162952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>挂机模拟经营：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新挂机模拟经营玩法，只需接单、种植、采集、制作。就能将你的饮料销售到全宇宙！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/6004dc0b9cbd79605310dc269835de23.poster.avif?t=1765162952\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/6004dc0b9cbd79605310dc269835de23.webm?t=1765162952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/6004dc0b9cbd79605310dc269835de23.mp4?t=1765162952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>种植农作物、花卉、水果：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择不同种类的植物进行种植，并通过生产这些植物来获得高价值的产品，提升你的农场收入。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/0194397f691724d9f36623aafbbb2cf8.poster.avif?t=1765162952\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/0194397f691724d9f36623aafbbb2cf8.webm?t=1765162952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/0194397f691724d9f36623aafbbb2cf8.mp4?t=1765162952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>动物饲养：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在陆地上饲养各种动物，收获它们的产品并进行加工，进一步增加资源和收益。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/7dce11128bade2ecf94467ce09b7025a.poster.avif?t=1765162952\" width=800 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/7dce11128bade2ecf94467ce09b7025a.webm?t=1765162952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/7dce11128bade2ecf94467ce09b7025a.mp4?t=1765162952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>沙盒建造：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由放置每一个地块，修建和装饰独一无二的岛屿。随着科技的发展，获得各种不同功能的建筑，收集和解锁各种物品，和机器人共同建成自动化运行的超大海岛农场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/7d27db912baef7c95c284ea8a09338f2.poster.avif?t=1765162952\" width=652 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/7d27db912baef7c95c284ea8a09338f2.webm?t=1765162952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196520/extras/7d27db912baef7c95c284ea8a09338f2.mp4?t=1765162952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
